^B@2^*BMike Lawrence: ^*N|cp||at|Bid two diamonds. You do not have a suit to show. The only bid you have to show points is two notrump. In this regard, I recommend you NEVER bid two notrump in response to an opening two club bid. It takes away bidding room, plus it can make the wrong hand declarer. Respond two diamonds and leave opener room to show his hand.|
